01:00:15,699 --> 01:00:18,527
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

1171
01:00:18,571 --> 01:00:20,268
I LOVE IT.
YOU DO?

1172
01:00:20,312 --> 01:00:22,009
[ LAUGHS ]

1173
01:00:26,318 --> 01:00:28,668
WOW.
SIT.

1174
01:00:28,712 --> 01:00:32,019
AND I MADE THAT MYSELF.

1175
01:00:32,063 --> 01:00:33,847
IT DIDN'T COME FROM A JAR.

1176
01:00:43,291 --> 01:00:45,685
UH... OH, NO. WHAT?
[ LAUGHS ]

1177
01:00:45,729 --> 01:00:48,209
WHAT?
IS IT TOO MUCH LIME?

1178
01:00:48,253 --> 01:00:50,037
[ COUGHING ]

1179
01:00:50,081 --> 01:00:51,256
[ LAUGHS ]

1180
01:00:51,299 --> 01:00:53,127
YOU KNOW, IT'S THE THOUGHT
THAT COUNTS.

1181
01:00:53,171 --> 01:00:54,433
[ Laughing ]
OKAY.

1182
01:00:54,476 --> 01:00:56,391
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
WELL, WINE, RIGHT?

1183
01:00:56,435 --> 01:00:59,307
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

1184
01:00:59,351 --> 01:01:00,874
THANK YOU.

1185
01:01:05,357 --> 01:01:07,925
THIS IS BEAUTIFUL.
THANK YOU.

1186
01:01:11,276 --> 01:01:13,191
[ Voice breaking ]
HONEY, I, UH...

1187
01:01:13,234 --> 01:01:15,759
I NEVER MEANT TO HURT YOU.
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

1188
01:01:15,802 --> 01:01:19,588
BUT I KNOW THAT I HAVE,
OVER AND OVER AGAIN,

1189
01:01:19,632 --> 01:01:22,679
AND I... IT MAKES ME
HATE MYSELF.

1190
01:01:22,722 --> 01:01:24,463
GEORGE, YOU DON'T HAVE TO...

1191
01:01:24,506 --> 01:01:25,812
NO, I DO, OKAY?

1192
01:01:25,856 --> 01:01:27,901
FROM THE FIRST MOMENT
I SAW YOU,

1193
01:01:27,945 --> 01:01:30,643
I KNEW THAT SOMEHOW,
SOMEWAY WE HAD TO BE TOGETHER,

1194
01:01:30,687 --> 01:01:33,472
I... I HAD TO HAVE YOU.

1195
01:01:33,515 --> 01:01:37,737
AND I CROSSED THE LINE
IN TRYING TO MAKE THAT HAPPEN,

1196
01:01:37,781 --> 01:01:40,697
TRYING TO KEEP YOU.

1197
01:01:44,439 --> 01:01:46,311
[ GASPING ]

1198
01:01:46,354 --> 01:01:48,356
GEORGE.

1199
01:01:55,233 --> 01:01:56,495
HOW CAN YOU DO THIS?

1200
01:01:56,538 --> 01:01:58,497
WHAT IS THE MATTER
WITH YOU?

1201
01:01:58,540 --> 01:02:00,412
KATIE WANTS HIM
TO COME HOME.

1202
01:02:00,455 --> 01:02:03,371
KATIE IS A CHILD.
SHE DOESN'T UNDERSTAND.

1203
01:02:03,415 --> 01:02:06,505
HE'S MADE CHANGES.
HE'S HAD COUNSELING.

1204
01:02:06,548 --> 01:02:07,680
THAT KIND OF BEHAVIOR
DOESN'T CHANGE

1205
01:02:07,724 --> 01:02:08,637
WITH A LITTLE COUNSELING.

1206
01:02:08,681 --> 01:02:10,248
TWO WEEKS AGO, YOU SAID

1207
01:02:10,291 --> 01:02:11,771
YOU WERE FALLING IN LOVE
WITH STEPHEN DREW.

1208
01:02:11,815 --> 01:02:13,642
DOESN'T MATTER ANYMORE.

1209
01:02:13,686 --> 01:02:17,255
HE DUMPED YOU, DIDN'T HE?

1210
01:02:17,298 --> 01:02:18,299
SON OF A BITCH.

1211
01:02:18,343 --> 01:02:20,475
DON'T.

1212
01:02:20,519 --> 01:02:22,739
DON'T RUIN IT.

1213
01:02:22,782 --> 01:02:25,176
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.

1214
01:02:25,219 --> 01:02:27,744
I'VE NEVER HAD ANYTHING
LIKE THAT BEFORE.

1215
01:02:27,787 --> 01:02:29,615
I'M GRATEFUL.

1216
01:02:29,658 --> 01:02:31,878
I WISH YOU'D WAKE UP.

1217
01:02:31,922 --> 01:02:35,447
I AM AWAKE, GINNY,
WIDE AWAKE.

1218
01:02:35,490 --> 01:02:38,189
THIS IS WHERE
I'M SUPPOSED TO BE.

1219
01:02:42,671 --> 01:02:45,152
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

1220
01:02:53,421 --> 01:02:56,555
HEY, MOM,
WHAT DO YOU THINK ABOUT

1221
01:02:56,598 --> 01:02:59,340
TAKING CHINESE FOOD
OUT TONIGHT?

1222
01:03:02,169 --> 01:03:03,692
SWEETIE, YOUR DAD AND I
HAVE BEEN TALKING.

1223
01:03:03,736 --> 01:03:06,826
[ SIGHS ]

1224
01:03:06,870 --> 01:03:08,480
WE'RE GONNA TRY
TO WORK IT OUT.

1225
01:03:11,657 --> 01:03:14,007
LOOK... [ SIGHS ]

1226
01:03:14,051 --> 01:03:15,966
I PROMISE YOU
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

1227
01:03:16,009 --> 01:03:19,230
NO, I-I'M REALLY GLAD
THAT YOU'RE TAKING HIM BACK.

1228
01:03:19,273 --> 01:03:21,623
YOU ARE?

1229
01:03:21,667 --> 01:03:23,974
YEAH. [ CHUCKLES ]

1230
01:03:24,017 --> 01:03:27,020
AND HE PROMISED ME THAT
HE WOULDN'T HURT YOU AGAIN.

1231
01:03:28,717 --> 01:03:30,850
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

1232
01:03:30,894 --> 01:03:32,809
[ LAUGHS ]

1233
01:03:34,898 --> 01:03:37,552
[ LAUGHS ]

1234
01:03:37,596 --> 01:03:38,858
OKAY.
YEAH.

1235
01:03:38,902 --> 01:03:39,859
GO ORDER.
YEAH.

1236
01:03:40,817 --> 01:03:42,862
I AM NOT A VICTIM.

1237
01:03:42,906 --> 01:03:45,691
MAYBE IT LOOKS LIKE I AM.

1238
01:03:45,734 --> 01:03:48,128
I KNOW PEOPLE IN TOWN
MIGHT THINK SO

1239
01:03:48,172 --> 01:03:50,261
IF THEY KNEW WHAT'S HAPPENED
IN THIS HOUSE.

1240
01:03:50,304 --> 01:03:53,960
BUT DEEP INSIDE ME,
I KNOW I'M NOT.

1241
01:03:54,004 --> 01:03:58,486
GEORGE DOESN'T BEAT ME
BECAUSE HE WANTS TO HURT ME.

1242
01:03:58,530 --> 01:04:01,315
HE DOES IT 'CAUSE
HE'S AFRAID TO LOSE ME.

1243
01:04:01,359 --> 01:04:03,404
WOW.

1244
01:04:03,448 --> 01:04:08,888
THE THING ABOUT GEORGE IS,
I UNDERSTAND HIM.

1245
01:04:12,849 --> 01:04:14,763
WE ALL NEED TO BE UNDERSTOOD.

1246
01:04:14,807 --> 01:04:16,374
I'LL NEVER
LET YOU GO AGAIN.

1247
01:04:24,643 --> 01:04:27,428
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

1248
01:04:27,472 --> 01:04:28,429
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

1249
01:04:28,473 --> 01:04:29,474
HELLO?

1250
01:04:29,517 --> 01:04:31,084
Stephen? Aaron Lance.

1251
01:04:31,128 --> 01:04:33,391
OH, HEY, AARON. THANKS SO MUCH
FOR CALLING ME BACK.

1252
01:04:33,434 --> 01:04:35,001
LISTEN... YOU REMEMBER
YOU TOLD ME

1253
01:04:35,045 --> 01:04:37,003
IF I EVER NEEDED A LAWYER
TO GIVE YOU A CALL?

1254
01:04:37,047 --> 01:04:38,657
I'm at your service, pastor.
What's up?

1255
01:04:38,700 --> 01:04:41,312
YEAH, WELL...
I'M CALLING YOU.

1256
01:04:41,355 --> 01:04:43,270
I'M GONNA BE LEAVING TOWN
FOR A WHILE.

1257
01:04:45,142 --> 01:04:46,447
HELLO, JIM.

1258
01:04:46,491 --> 01:04:47,927
HELLO, AARON.

1259
01:04:47,971 --> 01:04:49,537
AND HERE'S HAVERILL'S
FAVORITE SPITFIRE.

1260
01:04:49,581 --> 01:04:51,844
HELLO.
WHERE'S YOUR CLIENT?

1261
01:04:51,888 --> 01:04:53,150
OH, HE'S NOT COMING BACK

1262
01:04:53,193 --> 01:04:54,934
UNTIL HE'S ASSURED
HE WON'T BE ARRESTED.

1263
01:04:54,978 --> 01:04:58,068
WELL, THEN,
WE'LL JUST FIND HIM.

1264
01:04:58,111 --> 01:05:00,244
CATHERINE, WE ALL KNOW

1265
01:05:00,287 --> 01:05:03,377
YOU DON'T HAVE ENOUGH
TO GET EVEN AN INDICTMENT.

1266
01:05:03,421 --> 01:05:05,640
THIS ONLY GOES FORWARD
IF HE CONFESSES,

1267
01:05:05,684 --> 01:05:08,687
AND HE'S NOT GONNA CONFESS
TO A CRIME HE DID NOT COMMIT.

1268
01:05:08,730 --> 01:05:10,558
NOW, I UNDERSTAND

1269
01:05:10,602 --> 01:05:12,430
YOU'RE VERY PASSIONATE
ABOUT THIS CASE,

1270
01:05:12,473 --> 01:05:13,561
AND I COMMEND YOU FOR IT.

1271
01:05:13,605 --> 01:05:15,041
YOU'RE JUST WRONG.

1272
01:05:15,085 --> 01:05:16,869
WELL, WE'LL SEE.

1273
01:05:16,913 --> 01:05:19,872
IT'S ALWAYS VERY NICE
TO SEE YOU.
MM-HMM.

1274
01:05:19,916 --> 01:05:21,961
[ BIRDS SQUAWKING ]

1275
01:05:24,833 --> 01:05:25,922
[ DOG BARKING ]

1276
01:05:25,965 --> 01:05:27,662
OH. OOH.[ DOG GROWLING ]

1277
01:05:27,706 --> 01:05:29,664
LULA, NO.

1278
01:05:29,708 --> 01:05:31,753
HEY. HEY.

1279
01:05:31,797 --> 01:05:33,190
OH, KATIE, HI.

1280
01:05:33,233 --> 01:05:35,453
I'M REALLY SORRY
TO JUST STOP BY LIKE THIS,

1281
01:05:35,496 --> 01:05:37,368
BUT I REALLY NEED YOUR HELP.

1282
01:05:37,411 --> 01:05:39,631
IT'S ABOUT PASTOR DREW,
ISN'T IT?
YES.

1283
01:05:39,674 --> 01:05:43,504
LISTEN, UM...
COULD YOU JUST COME OUTSIDE?

1284
01:05:43,548 --> 01:05:44,853
CAN WE... CAN WE TALK?

1285
01:05:44,897 --> 01:05:48,901
YEAH. YEAH, SURE.

1286
01:05:48,945 --> 01:05:51,686
[ EXHALES HEAVILY ]

1287
01:05:51,730 --> 01:05:53,471
[ SIGHS ]

1288
01:05:53,514 --> 01:05:54,994
I MEAN, I'M NOT SURPRISED.

1289
01:05:55,038 --> 01:05:57,518
I KNOW YOU GUYS SEARCHED HIS
HOUSE AND EVERYTHING, BUT...

1290
01:05:57,562 --> 01:06:00,130
PASTOR DREW? REALLY?

1291
01:06:00,173 --> 01:06:02,959
ANYTHING YOU CAN THINK OF,
KATIE, ANYTHING AT ALL.

1292
01:06:03,002 --> 01:06:05,570
ALL I CAN THINK OF
IS HOW MUCH SHE LIKED HIM.

1293
01:06:05,613 --> 01:06:09,052
I MEAN,
SHE... REALLY LIKED HIM.

1294
01:06:11,880 --> 01:06:14,709
YOU KNEW ABOUT THE AFFAIR?

1295
01:06:14,753 --> 01:06:18,104
SHE TRIED TO HIDE IT,
BUT, I MEAN, I FIGURED IT OUT.

1296
01:06:18,148 --> 01:06:19,801
IS THAT WHY
YOU GUYS THINK IT'S HIM?

1297
01:06:19,845 --> 01:06:23,936
WELL, IT CERTAINLY
GIVES HIM MOTIVE, YES.

1298
01:06:23,980 --> 01:06:25,894
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

1299
01:06:25,938 --> 01:06:32,205
I HAD THIS, UH, DREAM
A COUPLE OF NIGHTS AGO.

1300
01:06:32,249 --> 01:06:36,296
AND, UM,
MY PARENTS WERE DEAD.

1301
01:06:36,340 --> 01:06:41,301
AND THEN LULA WAS LAPPING
THE BLOOD OFF MY DAD'S HEAD.

1302
01:06:41,345 --> 01:06:44,000
AND IT WAS REALLY DISGUSTING
AND IT FELT REALLY REAL

1303
01:06:44,043 --> 01:06:47,829
AND THEN WHEN I WOKE UP,
IT JUST... I GOT SICK AND...

1304
01:06:47,873 --> 01:06:51,659
KATIE, LISTEN.

1305
01:06:51,703 --> 01:06:56,360
WHEN THE POLICE GOT HERE,
LULA WAS OUTSIDE, OKAY?

1306
01:06:56,403 --> 01:06:58,710
SO, EVEN IF THAT SEEMED REAL
IN YOUR DREAM...

1307
01:06:58,753 --> 01:07:00,364
MM-HMM.

1308
01:07:00,407 --> 01:07:03,845
...IT DIDN'T HAPPEN
IN REAL LIFE, OKAY?

1309
01:07:03,889 --> 01:07:05,369
[ RAIN POUNDING ]

1310
01:07:07,893 --> 01:07:09,112
WAIT. OKAY.

1311
01:07:09,155 --> 01:07:11,679
LULA'S NEVER OUTSIDE
UNLESS SHE'S ON A LEASH.

1312
01:07:11,723 --> 01:07:16,032
SO, WHOEVER SHOT YOUR DAD
MUST HAVE LET HER OUT.

1313
01:07:16,075 --> 01:07:18,991
SHE WOULD HAVE ATTACKED
SOMEBODY THAT SHE DOESN'T KNOW,

1314
01:07:19,035 --> 01:07:20,427
ESPECIALLY AT THE HOUSE.

1315
01:07:20,471 --> 01:07:22,603
SHE DOESN'T LIKE STRANGERS,
AND SHE HATES MEN,

1316
01:07:22,647 --> 01:07:25,998
EXCEPT FOR DAD
AND PASTOR DREW.

1317
01:07:26,042 --> 01:07:30,089
SO, YOU'RE SAYING SHE WOULD
HAVE ATTACKED A STRANGER.

1318
01:07:30,133 --> 01:07:31,699
YEAH, SHREDDED THEM.

1319
01:07:31,743 --> 01:07:33,919
MY PARENTS
ALMOST GOT SUED ONCE.

1320
01:07:33,962 --> 01:07:38,097
BUT THE ONLY BLOOD IN THE HOUSE
BELONGED TO YOUR PARENTS.

1321
01:07:42,667 --> 01:07:43,581
[ SIGHS ]

1322
01:07:43,624 --> 01:07:45,104
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

1323
01:07:46,932 --> 01:07:49,935
KATIE...

1324
01:07:49,978 --> 01:07:53,939
LULA MUST HAVE KNOWN
YOUR FATHER'S KILLER.

1325
01:07:53,982 --> 01:07:57,682
SHE MUST HAVE.

1326
01:07:57,725 --> 01:08:00,641
OH.

1327
01:08:00,685 --> 01:08:03,209
DON'T LET IT,
LIKE, BE HIM 'C...

1328
01:08:03,253 --> 01:08:04,558
I'm so sorry.

1329
01:08:08,171 --> 01:08:11,435
PLEASE DON'T LET IT BE HIM.

1330
01:08:16,657 --> 01:08:17,963
[ PARKING BRAKE CLICKS ]

1331
01:08:18,006 --> 01:08:19,225
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

1332
01:08:19,269 --> 01:08:21,009
HI.Heather: YOU MADE IT.

1333
01:08:21,053 --> 01:08:22,837
YEAH.
THANKS FOR THE INVITE.

1334
01:08:22,881 --> 01:08:24,796
THANKS FOR COMING.

1335
01:08:24,839 --> 01:08:27,103
I'LL TAKE THAT.
SURE.

1336
01:08:27,146 --> 01:08:29,583
SO, COME ON BACK.

1337
01:08:29,627 --> 01:08:31,890
THIS PLACE IS AWFUL.

1338
01:08:31,933 --> 01:08:33,935
I MEAN,
IT LOOKS LIKE A SHACK.

1339
01:08:33,979 --> 01:08:35,198
IS IT HAUNTED?

1340
01:08:35,241 --> 01:08:37,113
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S MY REFUGE.

1341
01:08:37,156 --> 01:08:38,331
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

1342
01:08:38,375 --> 01:08:39,289
THANK YOU.
REALLY BEAUTIFUL.

1343
01:08:39,332 --> 01:08:40,855
OH, I READ YOUR BOOK.

1344
01:08:40,899 --> 01:08:41,987
UH-HUH?

1345
01:08:42,030 --> 01:08:43,075
AND I LIKED IT.

1346
01:08:43,119 --> 01:08:44,816
BUT...?

1347
01:08:44,859 --> 01:08:47,732
WELL, YOU TALK A LOT
ABOUT ILLUMINATION

1348
01:08:47,775 --> 01:08:51,736
AND CHERUBS AND SERAPHIM
AND FLYING MONKEYS.

1349
01:08:51,779 --> 01:08:55,000
IS THAT REALLY ALL YOU GOT
FROM MY BOOK?

1350
01:08:55,043 --> 01:08:58,177
YOU KNOW, I TALK ABOUT
GRIEF AND CLOSURE, TOO.

1351
01:09:00,658 --> 01:09:03,008
YEAH, I KNOW.
I LIKED THAT PART.

1352
01:09:03,051 --> 01:09:07,012
BUT YOU CAME.

1353
01:09:07,055 --> 01:09:10,494
SO YOU DON'T THINK
I'M A COMPLETE PHONY.

1354
01:09:10,537 --> 01:09:12,713
I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE A COMPLETE PHONY.

1355
01:09:12,757 --> 01:09:15,368
WHO AM I TO TALK?
I DON'T HAVE ANY ANSWERS.

1356
01:09:15,412 --> 01:09:17,240
I SPEND MY DAYS
COUNSELING PEOPLE,

1357
01:09:17,283 --> 01:09:19,024
AND I CAN BARELY
MANAGE MY OWN LIFE.

1358
01:09:19,067 --> 01:09:22,245
MM.

1359
01:09:22,288 --> 01:09:24,203
YEP.

1360
01:09:24,247 --> 01:09:26,336
LET'S GO FOR A WALK.

1361
01:09:26,379 --> 01:09:28,120
I'M GLAD YOU CAME.

1362
01:09:28,164 --> 01:09:29,382
I'M GLAD I CAME, TOO.

1363
01:09:39,827 --> 01:09:42,787
[ CHAIR CLATTERS ]

1364
01:09:42,830 --> 01:09:45,093
[ BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY ]

1365
01:09:56,888 --> 01:09:58,846
[ BOTH MOANING ]

1366
01:09:58,890 --> 01:10:00,761
ALICE.

1367
01:10:04,939 --> 01:10:06,854
YOU JUST CALLED ME ALICE.

1368
01:10:09,030 --> 01:10:10,858
DON'T.

1369
01:10:23,001 --> 01:10:24,568
[ SIGHS ]

1370
01:10:26,918 --> 01:10:28,398
I'M SORRY.

1371
01:10:31,357 --> 01:10:34,186
DID YOU LOVE HER?

1372
01:10:34,230 --> 01:10:35,361
I DID.

1373
01:10:35,405 --> 01:10:37,363
I DID LOVE HER.

1374
01:10:40,366 --> 01:10:42,499
AND YOU THOUGHT
YOU COULD SAVE HER.

1375
01:10:42,542 --> 01:10:45,241
I THOUGHT SHE WAS SAVING HERSELF
WHEN SHE LEFT GEORGE.

1376
01:10:48,244 --> 01:10:50,376
I JUST...
I COULDN'T HANDLE THAT.

1377
01:10:50,420 --> 01:10:53,988
I... I DON'T KNOW.

1378
01:10:54,032 --> 01:10:56,382
ALICE WAS PART
OF THE CONGREGATION.

1379
01:10:56,426 --> 01:10:57,905
[ SIGHS ]

1380
01:10:57,949 --> 01:10:59,255
SHE WAS IN THIS ABUSIVE
RELATIONSHIP.

1381
01:11:02,345 --> 01:11:05,261
SEEING THOSE SCARS...

1382
01:11:09,439 --> 01:11:15,053
THE BOTTOM LINE IS
THAT... I BROKE IT OFF,

1383
01:11:15,096 --> 01:11:18,796
SHE WENT BACK TO GEORGE,
AND HE KILLED HER.

1384
01:11:18,839 --> 01:11:21,015
THE TRUTH IS, I GUESS,

1385
01:11:21,059 --> 01:11:25,324
I DIDN'T REALLY REALIZE
THAT I TRULY LOVED HER

1386
01:11:25,368 --> 01:11:26,760
UNTIL IT WAS TOO LATE.

1387
01:11:29,023 --> 01:11:34,072
BEING IN THAT HOUSE,
ALL THE BLOOD,

1388
01:11:34,115 --> 01:11:37,031
LIFE DRAINED FROM HER BODY,

1389
01:11:37,075 --> 01:11:40,557
ALL I COULD THINK OF
WAS KATIE

1390
01:11:40,600 --> 01:11:43,211
AND HOW HER LIFE
AS SHE KNEW IT WAS OVER.

1391
01:11:43,255 --> 01:11:45,301
I HAD TO HELP HER.

1392
01:11:45,344 --> 01:11:48,042
EVEN IF MEANS
GOING TO JAIL, I...

1393
01:11:48,086 --> 01:11:50,828
[ SIGHS ]

1394
01:11:50,871 --> 01:11:52,351
I'M SORRY.

1395
01:11:55,093 --> 01:11:56,181
I SHOULD GO.

1396
01:11:56,224 --> 01:11:58,879
NO. STAY.

1397
01:11:58,923 --> 01:12:00,664
IS THAT ALL RIGHT?

1398
01:12:00,707 --> 01:12:05,408
YEAH, OF COURSE.
IT'S ALMOST MORNING.

1399
01:12:05,451 --> 01:12:08,019
WE'LL TALK MORE THEN.

1400
01:12:08,062 --> 01:12:09,847
THANK YOU.

1401
01:12:09,890 --> 01:12:12,458
MY BAG IN THE CAR.

1402
01:12:26,559 --> 01:12:30,520
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

1403
01:12:30,563 --> 01:12:33,479
[ Cellphone ringing ]

1404
01:12:33,523 --> 01:12:36,352
MRS. BENINCASA?

1405
01:12:48,581 --> 01:12:51,236
AH.
GOOD MORNING, PASTOR.

1406
01:12:51,279 --> 01:12:53,107
WE NEED TO TALK.
EMMET.

1407
01:12:53,151 --> 01:12:55,196
GENTLEMEN.

1408
01:12:55,240 --> 01:12:57,155
STEPHEN DREW,

1409
01:12:57,198 --> 01:12:59,244
YOU ARE UNDER ARREST FOR
THE MURDER OF GEORGE HAYWARD.

1410
01:12:59,287 --> 01:13:03,161
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

1411
01:13:03,204 --> 01:13:05,946
[ HANDCUFFS CLICKING ]

1412
01:13:17,654 --> 01:13:18,785
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

1413
01:13:22,398 --> 01:13:23,964
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

1414
01:13:24,008 --> 01:13:25,792
[ PARKING BRAKE CLICKS ]

1415
01:13:25,836 --> 01:13:29,535
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

1416
01:13:29,579 --> 01:13:33,496
Alice: STEPHEN,
WILL YOU BAPTIZE ME?

1417
01:13:33,539 --> 01:13:34,584
DID YOU HEAR ME?

1418
01:13:34,627 --> 01:13:36,716
SORRY. YES.

1419
01:13:36,760 --> 01:13:40,024
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

1420
01:13:40,067 --> 01:13:41,504
ALICE, I THINK ABOUT YOU
ALL THE TIME.

1421
01:13:41,547 --> 01:13:43,941
DON'T.

1422
01:13:43,984 --> 01:13:46,204
THIS ISN'T ABOUT YOU AND ME.

1423
01:13:46,247 --> 01:13:49,120
IT'S ABOUT A RECOMMITMENT
TO MY FAITH.

1424
01:13:49,163 --> 01:13:51,296
WHAT ABOUT GEORGE?
WHAT WILL HE THINK?

1425
01:13:51,339 --> 01:13:54,734
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN
WHAT GEORGE THINKS.

1426
01:13:54,778 --> 01:13:56,780
SO, YOU'LL TELL HIM?

1427
01:13:56,823 --> 01:13:58,869
IF HE ASKS.

1428
01:13:58,912 --> 01:14:00,392
YOU THINK THAT'S SMART?

1429
01:14:00,436 --> 01:14:03,003
I'M THE MASTER
OF MY OWN DESTINY, STEPHEN...

1430
01:14:03,047 --> 01:14:06,703
NOT YOU AND NOT GEORGE.

1431
01:14:06,746 --> 01:14:10,315
SO, WILL YOU BAPTIZE ME?

1432
01:14:12,622 --> 01:14:15,929
YES, ALICE,
I'LL BAPTIZE YOU.

1433
01:14:22,458 --> 01:14:23,807
CAN I HELP YOU?

1434
01:14:23,850 --> 01:14:26,418
YEAH, YOU CAN STAY AWAY
FROM MY WIFE.

1435
01:14:26,462 --> 01:14:27,288
HOW ABOUT THAT?

1436
01:14:29,465 --> 01:14:31,205
OH, THERE'S SO MANY THINGS

1437
01:14:31,249 --> 01:14:33,860
I'D LIKE TO SAY TO YOU
RIGHT NOW.

1438
01:14:33,904 --> 01:14:36,515
YEAH?
SO, WHAT'S STOPPING YOU?

1439
01:14:36,559 --> 01:14:38,996
RESPECT FOR YOUR WIFE.

1440
01:14:42,869 --> 01:14:46,482
I SAW YOU TALKING
TO HER TODAY IN TOWN.

1441
01:14:46,525 --> 01:14:49,441
I FOLLOWED HER.

1442
01:14:49,485 --> 01:14:52,879
YOUR COWARDICE
ASTONISHES ME.

1443
01:15:06,676 --> 01:15:08,765
THE MORE INVOLVED SHE'S GOTTEN
WITH YOU AND YOUR CHURCH,

1444
01:15:08,808 --> 01:15:10,680
THE MORE DISRESPECTFUL
SHE'S GOTTEN AT HOME.

1445
01:15:10,723 --> 01:15:13,509
CHERISH WHAT YOU HAVE.

1446
01:15:15,206 --> 01:15:17,643
[ GRUNTS ]

1447
01:15:17,687 --> 01:15:19,602
YOU PUT ANY MORE IDEAS
INTO MY WIFE'S HEAD,

1448
01:15:19,645 --> 01:15:21,038
AND I SWEAR TO GOD
I WILL KILL YOU.

1449
01:15:32,963 --> 01:15:34,051
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

1450
01:15:34,094 --> 01:15:36,401
HOW YOU DOING THESE DAYS?

1451
01:15:42,625 --> 01:15:45,671
I ACTUALLY FEEL PRETTY GUILTY
MOST OF THE TIME.

1452
01:15:45,715 --> 01:15:47,151
HOW COME?

1453
01:15:47,194 --> 01:15:48,718
SO, I JUST KEEP THINKING

1454
01:15:48,761 --> 01:15:50,197
THAT IF I DIDN'T GO
TO THAT CONCERT

1455
01:15:50,241 --> 01:15:51,851
AND IF I DIDN'T
LEAVE HER ALONE...

1456
01:15:51,895 --> 01:15:53,374
THEN THEY WOULDN'T
HAVE FOUGHT?

1457
01:15:53,418 --> 01:15:56,073
AND YOUR MOTHER
WOULD STILL BE ALIVE?

1458
01:15:56,116 --> 01:16:00,425
BUT THEY'D BOTH BE ALIVE,
YOU KNOW?

1459
01:16:00,468 --> 01:16:02,253
I MEAN, I COULDN'T BE THERE
ALL THE TIME.

1460
01:16:02,296 --> 01:16:04,951
AND THEY'D ACTUALLY
STOPPED FIGHTING,

1461
01:16:04,995 --> 01:16:07,998
SO I FIGURED JUST ONE NIGHT OUT
WITH MY FRIENDS WAS...

1462
01:16:08,041 --> 01:16:10,217
OF COURSE YOU DID, KATIE.

1463
01:16:10,261 --> 01:16:12,916
YOU'RE A KID.
YOU DESERVE THAT.

1464
01:16:15,135 --> 01:16:20,097
KATIE, IT WASN'T YOUR FAULT.
IT WASN'T.

1465
01:16:20,140 --> 01:16:22,186
MRS. BENINCASA, YOU THINK

1466
01:16:22,229 --> 01:16:24,884
THAT PASTOR DREW SHOT MY DAD,
DON'T YOU?

1467
01:16:24,928 --> 01:16:25,972
I'M SURE HE DID.

1468
01:16:28,105 --> 01:16:32,022
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

1469
01:16:32,065 --> 01:16:34,502
IT'S RIGHT AROUND HERE.

1470
01:16:34,546 --> 01:16:37,375
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

1471
01:16:39,943 --> 01:16:42,423
LET ME CHECK WITH THE OFFICE
AND I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

1472
01:16:42,467 --> 01:16:44,948
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE LETTING HIM GO.

1473
01:16:44,991 --> 01:16:47,080
YOU'VE GOT NO CONFESSION,
AND HE'S MADE BOND.

1474
01:16:47,124 --> 01:16:48,908
WE HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT TO LET HIM GO.

1475
01:16:48,952 --> 01:16:50,910
WE'LL NEVER BE ABLE
TO CONVICT HIM FOR MURDER

1476
01:16:50,954 --> 01:16:51,607
WITH WHAT WE HAVE.

1477
01:16:54,610 --> 01:16:55,393
I'M SORRY, CATHERINE.

1478
01:17:11,235 --> 01:17:14,847
[ DISHES RATTLE, BODY THUDS ]

1479
01:17:14,891 --> 01:17:18,024
[ GLASS BREAKS ]

1480
01:17:29,819 --> 01:17:31,472
[ CRYING ]

1481
01:17:34,127 --> 01:17:36,042
SO, WHAT, ARE YOU GONNA
PRESS CHARGES NOW?

1482
01:17:36,086 --> 01:17:37,653
IS THAT PART
OF YOUR NEW ATTITUDE?

1483
01:17:37,696 --> 01:17:39,306
I SHOULD.

1484
01:17:42,309 --> 01:17:45,051
YOU GOT BAPTIZED
TO SPITE ME?

1485
01:17:45,095 --> 01:17:48,664
OH, GOD, HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

1486
01:17:48,707 --> 01:17:50,709
THIS HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH YOU.

1487
01:17:50,753 --> 01:17:53,973
IT WAS ABOUT ME,
GEORGE, ME!

1488
01:17:54,017 --> 01:17:55,975
YOU DID IT TO PLEASE HIM,
AND YOU DID IT TO MOCK ME.

1489
01:17:56,019 --> 01:17:57,716
WELL, GUESS WHAT.

1490
01:17:57,760 --> 01:18:01,720
A MAN LIKE THAT DOESN'T
WANT A WHORE LIKE YOU!

1491
01:18:01,764 --> 01:18:05,202
YES, HE DID!
HE WANTED ME!

1492
01:18:05,245 --> 01:18:07,204
AND HE HAD ME IN THIS HOUSE,

1493
01:18:07,247 --> 01:18:09,336
IN THIS KITCHEN,
IN THE BEDROOM!

1494
01:18:09,380 --> 01:18:11,861
AND GUESS WHAT!
I LIKED IT!

1495
01:18:11,904 --> 01:18:12,905
AH!

1496
01:18:15,865 --> 01:18:17,649
[ GASPING ]

1497
01:18:17,693 --> 01:18:20,783
WHORE!

1498
01:18:20,826 --> 01:18:22,523
SHUT UP!

1499
01:18:31,184 --> 01:18:33,056
[ GASPING STOPS ]

1500
01:18:46,373 --> 01:18:48,985
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

1501
01:18:54,033 --> 01:18:55,513
[ GROANING LIGHTLY ]

1502
01:19:01,258 --> 01:19:03,956
[ GUNSHOT ]

1503
01:19:07,960 --> 01:19:10,267
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

1504
01:19:14,140 --> 01:19:16,403
HELLO, PASTOR.

1505
01:19:16,447 --> 01:19:20,930
YOU HAVE NO EVIDENCE,
CATHERINE.

1506
01:19:20,973 --> 01:19:22,801
DON'T YOU THINK IT'S TIME
TO LET IT GO?

1507
01:19:22,845 --> 01:19:26,892
NO, BECAUSE I THINK YOU'RE
GETTING AWAY WITH MURDER.

1508
01:19:26,936 --> 01:19:30,678
BUT I WON'T GIVE UP ON KATIE
LIKE YOU DID ON ALICE.

1509
01:19:30,722 --> 01:19:32,332
I'LL BE WATCHING YOU.

1510
01:19:36,859 --> 01:19:39,122
Pastor Drew:
WITH SUMMER ALMOST OVER,

1511
01:19:39,165 --> 01:19:41,385
LIFE SEEMS TO BE
RETURNING TO NORMAL.

1512
01:19:41,428 --> 01:19:44,475
THE CASE IS COLD, AND NO OTHER
SUSPECTS WERE EVER NAMED.

1513
01:19:44,518 --> 01:19:47,957
I DON'T SEE MUCH OF CATHERINE BENINCASA THESE DAYS.

1514
01:19:48,000 --> 01:19:51,308
NOT SURPRISINGLY, SHE NO LONGER
ATTENDS MY CHURCH.

1515
01:19:51,351 --> 01:19:55,312
I STILL THINK OF ALICE
EVERY DAY.

1516
01:19:55,355 --> 01:19:58,750
I NOW KNOW THAT WHAT I DID
WAS PART OF GOD'S PLAN.

1517
01:19:58,794 --> 01:20:01,100
MANY OF MY CONGREGANTS
HAVE STRUGGLED

1518
01:20:01,144 --> 01:20:03,363
TO PUT THE EVENTS OF THE PAST
MONTHS BEHIND THEM,

1519
01:20:03,407 --> 01:20:05,975
BUT WE'RE BEGINNING
TO FIND OUR WAY AGAIN.

1520
01:20:06,018 --> 01:20:09,152
HEALING HAS A FUNNY WAY
OF FINDING ITS WAY

1521
01:20:09,195 --> 01:20:11,110
THROUGH DARKNESS.

1522
01:20:11,154 --> 01:20:13,330
KATIE HAS A LOT OF GRIEVING
TO DO,

1523
01:20:13,373 --> 01:20:16,202
BUT LIVING AT GINNY'S
HAS DONE HER SOME GOOD.

1524
01:20:16,246 --> 01:20:19,205
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH, SHE KNOWS
I'LL ALWAYS BE THERE FOR HER.

1525
01:20:19,249 --> 01:20:20,816
Katie: HEY, PASTOR DREW.

1526
01:20:25,124 --> 01:20:26,473
THANKS AGAIN FOR EVERYTHING.

1527
01:20:26,517 --> 01:20:27,387
PROMISE ME
YOU'LL LET US KNOW

1528
01:20:27,431 --> 01:20:28,911
IF THERE'S ANYTHING YOU NEED.

1529
01:20:28,954 --> 01:20:30,042
NO, I WILL. I PROMISE.
[ CHUCKLES ]
OKAY.

1530
01:20:33,350 --> 01:20:35,787
GIVE ME THIS.

1531
01:20:35,831 --> 01:20:38,485
THANKS.

1532
01:20:38,529 --> 01:20:41,227
I AM GONNA MISS YOU
SO MUCH.

1533
01:20:41,271 --> 01:20:42,794
I'M GONNA MISS YOU, TOO.

1534
01:20:48,234 --> 01:20:50,193
DRIVE SAFE.

1535
01:20:53,979 --> 01:20:55,154
Katie: I'M GONNA MISS YOU
THE MOST.

1536
01:20:55,198 --> 01:20:55,938
[ DOG WHIMPERING ]

1537
01:20:55,981 --> 01:20:57,243
YEAH.

1538
01:21:02,945 --> 01:21:04,511
THANKS FOR DRIVING ME.

1539
01:21:04,555 --> 01:21:05,904
YOU KIDDING ME?
IT'S MY HONOR.

1540
01:21:05,948 --> 01:21:06,862
[ CHUCKLES ]

1541
01:21:11,562 --> 01:21:14,913
YOU MUST BE EXCITED...
COLBY.

1542
01:21:14,957 --> 01:21:16,436
YEAH.
MMM.

1543
01:21:16,480 --> 01:21:17,394
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

1544
01:21:17,437 --> 01:21:18,656
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

1545
01:21:20,397 --> 01:21:21,659
BYE.

1546
01:21:26,011 --> 01:21:28,927
GUYS?

1547
01:21:28,971 --> 01:21:32,235
MOM?

1548
01:21:32,278 --> 01:21:34,106
DAD?

1549
01:21:41,113 --> 01:21:43,420
Katie: THE HAYWARDS...

1550
01:21:43,463 --> 01:21:45,030
THEY APPEARED
TO HAVE IT ALL...

1551
01:21:58,000 --> 01:21:59,523
MOM?

1552
01:21:59,566 --> 01:22:00,959
...BLESSED WITH GOOD HEALTH...

1553
01:22:01,003 --> 01:22:03,396
MOM?

1554
01:22:03,440 --> 01:22:05,050
MOM?! MOM?!

1555
01:22:05,094 --> 01:22:06,443
MO...

1556
01:22:08,184 --> 01:22:11,100
MO...
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

1557
01:22:11,143 --> 01:22:11,970
...AND A BEAUTIFUL DAUGHTER,
KATIE...

1558
01:22:12,014 --> 01:22:14,016
DAD?

1559
01:22:14,059 --> 01:22:15,452
DAD? DAD, IT'S... DA...

1560
01:22:18,281 --> 01:22:20,761
[ GROANING LIGHTLY ]

1561
01:22:29,379 --> 01:22:31,642
...EVERY PARENT'S DREAM,

1562
01:22:31,685 --> 01:22:35,994
KIND-HEARTED, RESPONSIBLE,
AND SMART.

1563
01:22:36,038 --> 01:22:38,910
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

1564
01:22:40,433 --> 01:22:44,046
GEORGE OWNED A SUCCESSFUL CHAIN OF SPORTING-GOOD STORES

1565
01:22:44,089 --> 01:22:47,266
ACROSS THE STATE...
EVERY WOMAN'S DREAM.

1566
01:22:54,230 --> 01:22:58,277
ALICE WAS A HOMEMAKER,
AND SHE WAS ACTIVE IN CHURCH.

1567
01:23:02,455 --> 01:23:05,197
THE ALL-AMERICAN FAMILY.

1568
01:23:12,378 --> 01:23:14,380
BUT THAT'S THE TROUBLE OF BEING ON THE OUTSIDE, LOOKING IN...

1569
01:23:18,471 --> 01:23:19,777
YOU NEVER REALLY KNOW.

1570
01:23:30,222 --> 01:23:32,572
[ GUNSHOT ]

1571
01:23:32,616 --> 01:23:35,575
[ CRIES ]

1572
01:23:35,619 --> 01:23:38,056
[ GUN THUDS ]

1573
01:23:38,100 --> 01:23:39,536
[ Crying ] I DIDN'T KNOW
WHERE ELSE TO GO.

1574
01:23:39,579 --> 01:23:41,581
I COULDN'T GO BACK TO TINA'S.

1575
01:23:41,625 --> 01:23:43,061
YOU'RE SAFE HERE.
YOU'RE SAFE HERE.
YOU CAN TRUST ME.

1576
01:23:43,105 --> 01:23:44,889
PUT YOUR HANDS UNDER THERE.

1577
01:23:44,932 --> 01:23:47,022
SO, ARE WE... ARE WE
SUPPOSED TO CALL THE POLICE?

1578
01:23:47,065 --> 01:23:48,588
NO, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO, NO.

1579
01:23:48,632 --> 01:23:49,676
WE'RE NOT GONNA CALL
THE POLICE.

1580
01:23:49,720 --> 01:23:51,635
YOU'RE NOT GONNA GO
TO JAIL.

1581
01:23:51,678 --> 01:23:53,550
I WON'T LET YOU RUIN
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

1582
01:23:56,379 --> 01:24:00,296
I'LL MAKE IT LOOK LIKE
YOUR FATHER SHOT HIMSELF.

1583
01:24:00,339 --> 01:24:02,080
YEAH, BUT WHAT IF THEY
FIND OUT THAT HE DIDN'T?

1584
01:24:02,124 --> 01:24:05,692
IF THEY SUSPECT ANYONE,
WE'LL LET THEM SUSPECT ME.

1585
01:24:05,736 --> 01:24:07,477
THEN YOU'LL GO TO JAIL,
RIGHT?

1586
01:24:07,520 --> 01:24:09,087
I KNOW.

1587
01:24:09,131 --> 01:24:10,697
ALL RIGHT, NOW,
WHAT ABOUT TINA?

1588
01:24:10,741 --> 01:24:12,308
DOES SHE KNOW YOU'RE GONE?

1589
01:24:12,351 --> 01:24:14,136
NO, SHE WAS ASLEEP
WHEN I LEFT.

1590
01:24:14,179 --> 01:24:15,659
I JUST WANTED TO GET
MY COMPUTER.

1591
01:24:15,702 --> 01:24:16,573
ALL RIGHT, THEN YOU NEED
TO GET BACK TO TINA'S,

1592
01:24:16,616 --> 01:24:18,096
AND I'LL TAKE CARE OF THIS.

1593
01:24:18,140 --> 01:24:19,402
YOU'D DO THAT FOR ME?

1594
01:24:19,445 --> 01:24:21,273
I WOULD.
AND I WILL.

1595
01:24:30,152 --> 01:24:31,283
THE POLICE ARE STARTING
TO SUSPECT ME,

1596
01:24:31,327 --> 01:24:32,719
WHICH IS A GOOD THING.

1597
01:24:32,763 --> 01:24:34,156
SO, IF THEY QUESTION YOU,
INCRIMINATE ME.

1598
01:24:34,199 --> 01:24:35,070
YEAH, BUT THEN
YOU'RE GONNA GET ARRESTED.

1599
01:24:48,126 --> 01:24:50,172
THEN YOU'RE GOING TO JAIL,
AND I DON'T WANT THAT.

1600
01:24:50,215 --> 01:24:51,825
THIS WHOLE THING'S MY FAULT,
ANYWAY.

1601
01:24:51,869 --> 01:24:54,176
THEY DON'T HAVE ENOUGH EVIDENCE
TO CONVICT ME,

1602
01:24:54,219 --> 01:24:56,265
BUT I WANT THEM TO THINK
THAT I DID IT.

1603
01:24:56,308 --> 01:24:59,050
LISTEN... THE ONLY WAY THAT
YOUR MOM WON'T DIE IN VAIN

1604
01:24:59,094 --> 01:25:00,486
IS IF YOU LIVE A HAPPY LIFE.

1605
01:25:00,530 --> 01:25:02,227
I WANT TO GIVE YOU
THAT CHANCE.

1606
01:25:02,271 --> 01:25:03,489
YEAH, BUT...

1607
01:25:03,533 --> 01:25:04,490
JUST DO WHAT I TELL YOU.

1608
01:25:08,190 --> 01:25:10,017
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

1609
01:25:13,108 --> 01:25:16,198
THANKS AGAIN FOR EVERYTHING,
PASTOR DREW.

1610
01:25:22,204 --> 01:25:24,162
I'D DO IT AGAIN
IN A HEARTBEAT.

1611
01:25:29,602 --> 01:25:34,390
IF I LIVE TO BE OLD, I KNOW
I'LL HAVE A TON OF REGRETS,

1612
01:25:34,433 --> 01:25:36,435
BUT PUTTING A BULLET
IN MY DAD'S HEAD

1613
01:25:36,479 --> 01:25:38,133
WON'T EVER BE ONE OF THEM.

